The recurring ''Simpsons'' character [[Otto Mann]] was modeled on Wolodarsky's appearance.<ref name="Kogen">{{cite video | people=Kogen, Jay|date=2001|title=The Simpsons season 1 DVD commentary for the episode "Homer's Odyssey"| medium=DVD|publisher=20th Century Fox}}</ref>
